    <item>
      <title>企业敦促下一届英国政府减少脱欧贸易摩擦</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/business-urges-next-uk-government-to-cut-brexit-trade-friction</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国工业联合会敦促下一届英国政府缓解贸易摩擦以促进经济增长，这使得英国脱欧后与欧盟的关系成为焦点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/business-urges-next-uk-government-to-cut-brexit-trade-friction</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普将于 10 月 4 日上诉佐治亚州，选举前审判将以失败告终</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/trump-georgia-appeal-set-for-oct-4-dooming-pre-election-trial</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 要求将富尔顿县地方检察官法尼·威利斯 (Fani Willis) 调离佐治亚州选举干预案的上诉，审理时间暂定于 10 月 4 日，这使得在 11 月 5 日美国总统大选之前进行审判几乎不可能。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-03/trump-georgia-appeal-set-for-oct-4-dooming-pre-election-trial</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 03 Jun 2024 22:16:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
